{"id":24118,"date":"2016-12-05T14:25:51","date_gmt":"2016-12-05T10:25:51","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/?p=24118"},"modified":"2019-06-22T15:05:49","modified_gmt":"2019-06-22T11:05:49","slug":"hold-fast-to-the-quran","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/12\/05\/hold-fast-to-the-quran\/","title":{"rendered":"Hadith on Quran: Hold fast to the Quran, you will never go astray"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Jubayr ibn Mut&#8217;am reported: We were with the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, and he said, \u201c<strong>Do you not bear witness that there is no God but Allah without any partner, that I am the messenger of Allah, and that the Quran has come from Allah<\/strong>?\u201d We said, \u201cOf course.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201c<strong>Then rejoice, for one end of this Quran is in the hand of Allah and the other is in your hands, so hold fast to it. Verily, you will never be ruined or led astray ever again.<\/strong>\u201d<\/p>\n<p>Source: Musnad al-Bazza\u0304r 3421<\/p>\n<p>Grade: <strong><em>Sahih<\/em><\/strong> (authentic) according to Al-Albani<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\">\u0639\u0646 \u062c\u0628\u064a\u0631 \u0628\u0646 \u0645\u0637\u0639\u0645 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0643\u064f\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0627 \u0645\u064e\u0639\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u0628\u0650\u0627\u0644\u0652\u062c\u064f\u062d\u0652\u0641\u064e\u0629\u0650 \u0641\u064e\u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e<strong> \u0623\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0633\u064e \u062a\u064e\u0634\u0652\u0647\u064e\u062f\u064f\u0648\u0646\u064e \u0623\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0644\u064e\u0627 \u0625\u0650\u0644\u064e\u0647\u064e \u0625\u0650\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0627 \u0627\u06